states of consciousness.

00:19:16.600 --> 00:19:18.850 align:middle line:10%
And one of the ones
that's very powerful

00:19:18.850 --> 00:19:20.560 align:middle line:10%
is holotropic breathing.

00:19:20.560 --> 00:19:24.890 align:middle line:84%
