00:20:37.490 --> 00:20:39.980 align:middle line:84%
There's another
technique or technology

00:20:39.980 --> 00:20:43.580 align:middle line:84%
called EMDR, eye
movement desensitization

00:20:43.580 --> 00:20:44.900 align:middle line:90%
and reprocessing.

00:20:44.900 --> 00:20:46.580 align:middle line:90%
Just remember EMDR.

00:20:46.580 --> 00:20:49.580 align:middle line:10%
EMDR is a spiritual
reset mode where

00:20:49.580 --> 00:20:52.280 align:middle line:10%
