sessions to get over something

00:21:10.640 --> 00:21:11.810 align:middle line:90%
that you're really stuck on.

00:21:11.810 --> 00:21:15.170 align:middle line:84%
And sometimes it takes a year to
clear out a lot of your trauma.

00:21:15.170 --> 00:21:17.780 align:middle line:10%
You can also, as a
spiritual hack a way

00:21:17.780 --> 00:21:21.470 align:middle line:10%
