00:21:50.640 --> 00:21:51.890 align:middle line:10%
So just be careful.

00:21:51.890 --> 00:21:53.780 align:middle line:10%
Don't rely on psychedelics.

00:21:53.780 --> 00:21:57.290 align:middle line:84%
If you have to do
ayahuasca 100 plus times

00:21:57.290 --> 00:22:00.480 align:middle line:84%
