after the fifth time.

00:22:04.830 --> 00:22:07.740 align:middle line:84%
These are things that
open a doorway for you

00:22:07.740 --> 00:22:09.510 align:middle line:90%
so that you can do the work.

00:22:09.510 --> 00:22:11.570 align:middle line:84%
But if you rely on
psychedelics to do the work,

00:22:11.570 --> 00:22:14.240 align:middle line:84%
they are not a
spiritual technology.

00:22:14.240 --> 00:22:16.790 align:middle line:84%
They're actually a spiritual
bypassing technology.

00:22:16.790 --> 00:22:18.540 align:middle line:84%
This is rampant in
the world today.

00:22:18.540 --> 00:22:19.790 align:middle line:90%
So they're an important tool.

00:22:19.790 --> 00:22:20.840 align:middle line:90%
Be careful.

00:22:20.840 --> 00:22:25.430 align:middle line:84%
Follow properly trained
people, not podcasters.

00:22:25.430 --> 00:22:28.493 align:middle line:84%
And finally, one of the most
impactful spiritual hacks

00:22:28.493 --> 00:22:30.410 align:middle line:84%
that I've come across
in my life, the reason I

00:22:30.410 --> 00:22:34.790 align:middle line:84%
