00:22:41.150 --> 00:22:45.620 align:middle line:84%
And what I do then is I train
the brain out of that pattern.

00:22:45.620 --> 00:22:50.240 align:middle line:84%
And the combination of
simultaneously doing EEG,

00:22:50.240 --> 00:22:51.980 align:middle line:84%
so you can see what
your brain's doing

00:22:51.980 --> 00:22:54.500 align:middle line:84%
