in your life, including trauma.

00:22:58.670 --> 00:23:01.160 align:middle line:10%
And it lets you choose
the state you're in

00:23:01.160 --> 00:23:03.480 align:middle line:10%
based on what the EEG is doing.

00:23:03.480 --> 00:23:05.810 align:middle line:84%
So it's not about just hooking
your brain up and trying

00:23:05.810 --> 00:23:07.850 align:middle line:84%
something, it's about
hooking your brain up

00:23:07.850 --> 00:23:10.880 align:middle line:84%
while I teach you
the reset process

00:23:10.880 --> 00:23:12.480 align:middle line:90%
that we talked about earlier.

00:23:12.480 --> 00:23:14.390 align:middle line:84%
And then you can see
how your brain changes.

00:23:14.390 --> 00:23:17.150 align:middle line:84%
And you can correlate, oh,
when my body feels like this,

00:23:17.150 --> 00:23:18.470 align:middle line:90%
my brain is doing that.

00:23:18.470 --> 00:23:20.420 align:middle line:90%
Now I know how to do it.

